products.name: NetBank Saver
products.description: An online savings account with the flexibility to move money in and out of your linked CommBank transaction account using NetBank or the CommBank app.

products.name: Youthsaver Account
products.description: Designed to help teach saving skills to under 18s, our Youthsaver account offers bonus interest for reaching saving goals.

products.name: GoalSaver
products.description: Be rewarded with a variable bonus interest rate for saving regularly each month.

products.name: Pensioner Security
products.description: A flexible account that keeps your retirement savings or pension income safe and working for you.

products.name: Smart Access
products.description: An everyday bank account, giving you access to unlimited electronic transactions and features to help your spending and bills stay on track. Plus if you meet certain criteria, we'll waive your $4 monthly account fee.

products.name: Streamline Basic
products.description: An everyday bank account for health care or pensioner concession card holders.

products.name: Private Bank Account
products.description: The Commonwealth Private Bank Account is an exclusive transaction account for Commonwealth Private clients.

products.name: Standard Term Deposit
products.description: Feel confident knowing exactly how much your money will earn. Lock-in a competitive interest rate from as short as 1 month to as long as 5 years.

products.name: Business Transaction Account
products.description: An everyday business bank account that you can open online, which provides unlimited electronic transactions and 20 assisted transactions on a monthly basis for customers on the $10 monthly account fee pricing option. Fees and charges will apply if you exceed this amount. Customers with the $0 monthly account fee pricing option will not have included assisted transactions - each assisted transaction will be chargeable. Please note Access, CommBiz and NetBank Service Fees may apply and are excluded from the unlimited electronic transactions.

products.name: Business Online Saver
products.description: A business savings account that can help you manage cash flow and set aside money for tax payments.

products.name: Standard Business Cheque Account - Interest Bearing Option
products.description: Transaction accounts that pays interest above minimum balances.

products.name: Corporate Low Rate card
products.description: Designed for medium businesses wishing to manage their cash flow by paying down larger items over time. Options to monitor employee expenses, set limits and access expense reports in order to minimise costs.

products.name: Corporate Interest Free Days card
products.description: Designed for medium to large businesses wanting to maximise cash flow with interest free days on purchases, monitor employee expenses, set transaction limits and access expense reports in order to track, analyse and forecast expenses.

products.name: Corporate charge card
products.description: Ideal for large organisations with significant expenses. You can set spending limits and access expense reports to monitor spending and forecast costs.

products.name: Virtual Cards
products.description: Virtual Cards are a streamlined travel and procurement management solution, which provides large businesses the ability to take advantage of extended payment terms, transaction level payment security, and transaction level data through the deployment of single-use virtual cards.

products.name: Procurement Management Account
products.description: A Procurement Management Account is a corporate card 'account' (16 digit card number) assigned to an organisation or business unit, which allows multiple authorised users to transact on the account. It is primarily used for a large volume of transactions (e.g. high volumes of travel bookings) or high value procurement transactions (e.g. strategic suppliers).

products.name: Diamond Awards credit card
products.description: A credit card that rewards your everyday spend, where you can earn up to 1 million points per year with the added benefit of international travel insurance.

products.name: Low Rate credit card
products.description: With a low interest rate on purchases, our Low Rate credit card makes it easier to pay off purchases over time.

products.name: Low Rate Gold credit card
products.description: Stay in control of your finances with our low purchase interest rate, plus handy extras like international travel insurance.

products.name: Low Fee credit card
products.description: Enjoy the flexibility and convenience of a credit card with a low annual fee.

products.name: Low Fee Gold
products.description: Enjoy the flexibility and convenience of a credit card with no annual fee in the first year and included international travel insurance (restrictions, exclusions (including for pre-existing medical conditions and persons aged 80 years or over), limits, sub-limits and excesses apply).

products.name: Awards credit card
products.description: For customers who want a lower annual fee and credit limit, but still like to earn Awards points.

products.name: Platinum Awards credit card
products.description: A credit card with the opportunity to earn Awards points and take advantage of extras like international travel insurance.

products.name: Low Rate credit card
products.description: Ideal for small business owners looking for a line of credit with a competitive interest rate and no annual fee. Note, this product does not include an interest free day period.

products.name: Interest-Free Days credit card
products.description: Designed for those looking for a card with a competitive interest-free period to help with business cash flow.

products.name: Business Awards credit card
products.description: Perfect for those looking for a competitive interest-free period on purchases and to reward themselves for business purchases.

products.name: Business Platinum Awards credit card
products.description: Earn 1 Awards point for every dollar you spend on your business expenses.

products.name: CommBank Essentials credit card
products.description: A simple card with our lowest rate on purchases, helping you stay in control.

products.name: Ultimate Awards credit card
products.description: Our most rewarding credit card with uncapped points earning potential, exclusive travel benefits and no monthly fee for eligible customers.

products.name: CommBank Neo Card
products.description: It's a new way to pay! An interest-free credit card without any late fees or surprise charges - just a flat monthly fee. Say goodbye to complex percentages and calculations.

products.name: Secured Car Loan
products.description: Unlock the value of your car for a reduced interest rate.

products.description: Stay in control with a fixed interest rate and fixed repayments for the life of the loan

products.name: Variable Rate Personal Loan
products.description: Get a competitive rate and have the flexibility to make additional repayments at any time without a fee.

products.name: Personal overdrafts
products.description: A personal overdraft can help you manage your cash flow by giving you access to additional funds (up to an approved limit) when you need it.

products.name: Everyday Offset
products.description: Everyday Offset is a feature of our Complete Access Transaction account which is linked to an eligible home loan, and account holder(s) must also be account holders of the linked home loan. Interest is not charged on the part of the Home Loan balance equal to the Transaction account. Full terms and conditions for transaction and savings accounts are available at CommBank.com.au or from any branch of the Commonwealth Bank. Fees and charges apply.

products.name: Travel Money Card
products.description: The Travel Money Card is a prepaid Visa card. You can load and reload up to 13 available currencies onto your card for your personal use when you travel.

products.name: CommBank AdvancePay
products.description: CommBank AdvancePay gives you access to money you expect to be paid, before your next pay day. It is a short term facility applied to your everyday account as a temporary limit.

products.name: -- About App --
products.description:
Hope you enjoyed CBA product details on your wrist (fitbit) !

`My Bank -AU-9` app displays products offered by CBA Bank (Australia).

Data is provided available as per Consumer Data Right (ACCC), Australia (alos known as Open Banking).

List of products displayed may not contain all the products currently offered by the bank.
Hence, for making any financial decision always go to : https://www.CBA.com.au/
